%N A397709 Number of face-connected components of n polyhedral cells in the sphenoid hendecahedral honeycomb, up to translation.
%C A397709 a(n)/A397708(n) tends to 24, the order of the point group of the honeycomb.
%e A397709 The honeycomb has 12 cells per translation-fundamental domain, so a(1) = 12.
%Y A397709 Cf. A397708 (counted up to rotation and reflection as well), A385028, A001931.
